Testimonials

DUNE KRISHNA SAI MANIKANTA,, B. Tech (CSD)

Choosing KIET, KORANGI, was one of the best decisions I ever took. I feel grateful for being able to explore my engineering life to the fullest. I thank my faculty, management, and placement cell for showing me a clear career path and guiding me to get placed. I cherish the unmatched passion for giving the best to a student.

POLISETI HARSHITH SATYA SAI, B. Tech (CSD)

Feel delighted to receive an offer from Accolite Digital Pvt. Ltd, I could achieve this only with the constant support and nurturing from the faculty and friendly competition between peers at KIET Institutions, Kakinada. I want to thank the placement team for helping me get this opportunity.
